  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Speech is a very important mode of communication, its absence or any abnormality develops an inability to express and to understand the person&apos;s feeling. This center works with students with multiple disabilities especially those with mental disabilities who have severe speech problems.  We treat about 150 children a month and with this facility, many can benefit by speech therapy. Your help will bring much-needed equipment to treat broader aspects of speech irregularities using AAC materials.</narrative>
  </description>
